data.description: GREAT INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY!!! Whether you're looking for your family, or as an investment property, 318 Brettonwood has it all! FULLY RENOVATED! With all the original charm & character in tact - original hard wood floors + built in cabinetry. Proximity to Ft. Sam Houston, downtown SA, major highways, shopping, local restaurants & schools...this is a great home to live in or hold as a SFR  investment. The garage has been enclosed for the addition of a 4th bedroom or family room/den. The covered patio has a beautiful tile mosaic design and plenty of shade to stay cool during those hot summer months. Adding 5K in seller concessions. This home is MOVE-IN READY!
